{"arkId":"cl010319884","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010319884","modified ":"2025-11-18","title":"Coupe au d\u00e9cor radi\u00e9 et inscrit","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"Coupe (Vase, r\u00e9cipient)"},{"type":"Titre","value":"Coupe au d\u00e9cor radi\u00e9 et inscrit"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : XIIIe si\u00e8cle (1200 - 1300)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1200,"endYear":1300,"imprecision":"","text":"XIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MAO 242","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Arts de l\u0027Islam","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; \u0627\u06cc \u062f\u0644 \u0637\u0645\u0639 \u0627\u0632 \u062c\u0641\u0627 \u067e\u0631\u0633\u062a\u06cc \u0628\u0631 \u062f\u0627\u0631 \/ \u0647\u0634\u06cc\u0627\u0631 \u0634\u0648 \u0627\u0645\u06cc\u062f \u0632 \u0645\u0633\u062a\u06cc \u0628\u0631\u062f\u0627\u0631 \/ \u062f\u0631 \u06a9\u0627\u0631 \u062e\u0644\u0627[\u0635 \u062a\u0648 \u062f\u0639\u06cc \u062e\u0648\u0627\u0647\u0645] \u06a9\u0631\u062f \/  \u0627\u06cc [\u067e\u0627\u06cc \u0632 \u062c\u0627\u06cc] \u0628\u0631\u0641\u062a \u062f\u0633\u062a\u06cc \u0628\u0631\u062f\u0627\u0631\r ; Lu par Abdullah Ghouchani, 2002\r ; Lecture de l\u0027inscription incompl\u00e8te : formule de voeu au possesseur, des parties effac\u00e9es par les restaurations. AG signale qu\u0027il a lu cette inscription sur deux autres pi\u00e8ces lustr\u00e9es.\r ; L\u0027auteur du quatrain est Muj\u012br od-D\u012bn Bilq\u0101n\u012b  \u0645\u062c\u06cc\u0631\u0627\u0644\u062f\u06cc\u0646 \u0628\u06cc\u0644\u0642\u0627\u0646\u06cc. Le quatrain fait partie de son Div\u00e2n et a \u00e9t\u00e9 publi\u00e9 dans \u0627\u0646\u062a\u0634\u0627\u0631\u0627\u062a \u062f\u0627\u0646\u0634\u06af\u0627\u0647 \u062a\u0628\u0631\u06cc\u0632 \u06f1\u06f3\u06f5\u06f8, \u00e9dition \u0635\u06f4.\u06f3. \r ; On note cependant des diff\u00e9rences entre le texte du Div\u00e2n et celui de l\u0027inscription c\u00e9ramique. note : Bilq\u0101n est un village en Azerba\u00efjan ou en Russie selon Abdullah Ghouchani\r ; Translitt\u00e9ration : ay dil \u1e6dam\u02bf az \u01e7af\u0101-parast\u012b bard\u0101r \/ hu\u0161y\u0101r \u0161\u016b um\u012bd zi mast\u012b bard\u0101r \/ dar k\u0101r \u1e96[al\u0101\u1e63 t\u016b da\u02bf\u012b \u1e96v\u0101ham] kard \/ ay [p\u0101y zi \u01e7\u0101y] biraft dast\u012b bard\u0101r\r ; Traduction : Oh coeur, renonce \u00e0 la cruaut\u00e9 \/ Soit sobre et abandonne l\u0027ivresse \/ Je prierai pour ton salut \/ Les jambes se d\u00e9robent, renonce ! (Trad. A.S. Daure, d\u0027apr\u00e8s A. Moghani)\r ; Nature du texte : Po\u00e9sie (Texte litt\u00e9raire) ; V\u0153ux\r ; Langue : persan","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"8,6","displayDimension":"8,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"20,7","displayDimension":"20,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"0,3","displayDimension":"0,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"0,4","displayDimension":"0,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"9","displayDimension":"9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : C\u00e9ramique\r\nMat\u00e9riau\/Technique : C\u00e9ramique (p\u00e2te siliceuse), d\u00e9cor peint sous gla\u00e7ure transparente","pla